      "message": "yeah, that\u0027s unfortunate, and the biggest downside of the current approach. Errors are delayed and require looking through logs*, and it\u0027s generally easy to break someone\u0027s production code accidentally by adding their service account wrongly to a group.\n\nNevertheless, I think `cost \u003c benefit` for this CL.",
